[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボス！　聞き込んだところ、獣人娘行方不明事件は\nこの辺りでも噂になっていました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00842",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そうか。それで？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00843",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "え、えっと……みんな「怖いなー」って\n言っていました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00844",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……そうか、ご苦労",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00845",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ちょ、ちょっと……余計なことかもしれないけど、\nあの子、聞き込みに向いてないんじゃ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00846",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "人の言うこと全部信じてるっていうか、\n鵜呑みにしてるっていうか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00847",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "忠告、感謝する。言いたいことは分かるし、\n実際その通りでもあるのだが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00848",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "あれはあれで、私にはできない方法で\n情報を稼いでくるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00849",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そうなの？　ちょっと信じられないけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00850",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "すぐに分かる。\nおーい、タイニー。世間話のほうはどうだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00851",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "世間話ですか？\nそういえば最近はお魚が安いんだそうですよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00852",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "なんでも王妃様が肉を食べたいってわがまま言って\n肉の値段が高騰、その煽りで魚が安くなってるとか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00853",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ほう、王妃が、わがままねえ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00854",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "王妃様は前からわがまま放題で、今回の行方不明事件も\n若い娘の美貌に嫉妬して消してるんじゃないかって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00855",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……と、このように\n妙に気になる情報を聞き出したりもする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00856",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "あのほんわかとした雰囲気が、\n警戒心を解くってことか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00857",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、そうだ！　それと、ボスたちも\n飴ちゃんいります？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00858",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "タイニーが聞き込みしてたらもらったんだって。\n甘くて美味しー♪",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00859",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "おじいちゃん、いっぱいくれたんですよ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00860",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ゆえに、年寄りや子どもの受けもいい。\n私だと怖がられる相手からも聞き込みができる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00861",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "多少の短所程度、長所があればいくらでも補える",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00862",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "おお……器が広い。\n上司として色々考えてるんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00863",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そんなことはないさ。単に、タイニーと組むことは\n物事を多角的に見るのに適している、というだけの話だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00864",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "またボスがなんか難しいことを言い始めましたねぇ。\nなんか聞いてると眠くなって……ふわぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00865",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちょ、ちょっとタイニー！　こんなとこで寝ちゃダメ！\n砂が入るし、干からびちゃうって！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00866",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "しかしのびのび育てるというのも難しくてな……\nのびのびすぎるというか……若者は難しいな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00867",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "エルスも十分若いと思うし、これは世代の問題とは\nまた別な気もするけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00868",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "本当に、よくあのヌルスラでこんなに純粋な娘が\n生き延びてこられたものだ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00869",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]